.637">in</span> <span begin="24.637" end="25.022">the</span> <span begin="25.022" end="25.835">light</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在月光下闪着柔和的光</span></p><p begin="26.543" end="29.508" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="26.543" end="26.775">It</span> <span begin="26.775" end="27.148">takes</span> <span begin="27.148" end="27.656">my</span> <span begin="27.656" end="28.125">breath</span> <span begin="28.125" end="29.508">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无暇的美丽令人窒息</span></p><p begin="29.957" end="32.575" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.957" end="30.193">Wish</span> <span begin="30.193" end="30.552">they</span> <span begin="30.552" end="30.992">could</span> <span begin="30.992" end="31.393">see</span> <span begin="31.393" end="31.899">you</span> <span begin="31.899" end="32.575">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可惜他们永远不曾见过</span></p><p begin="33.353" end="36.045" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.353" end="33.906">Without</span> <span begin="33.906" end="34.399">your</span> <span begin="34.399" end="35.309">precious</span> <span begin="35.309" end="36.045">crown</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">放下傲慢和戒备的你</span></p><p begin="36.764" end="39.560" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.764" end="37.173">It</span> <span begin="37.173" end="37.836">only</span> <span begin="37.836" end="38.362">weighs</span> <span begin="38.362" end="38.772">you</span> <span begin="38.772" end="39.560">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是如此的令人着迷</span></p><p begin="40.719" end="42.529" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.719" end="42.529">Whoa</span></p><p begin="43.153" end="49.839" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="43.153" end="44.101">Your</span> <span begin="44.101" end="45.736">naked</span> <span begin="45.736" end="46.674">soul</span> <span begin="46.674" end="47.371">is</span> <span begin="47.371" end="49.839">beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的美丽出淤泥而不染</span></p><p begin="50.090" end="56.475" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="50.090" end="50.958">You&apos;re</span> <span begin="50.958" end="51.788">not</span> <span begin="51.788" end="53.527">broken</span> <span begin="53.527" end="54.397">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="54.397" end="56.475">beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你没有想象中那样脆弱，你坚强的性格是最美的盛装</span></p><p begin="56.963" end="1:03.517" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="56.963" end="57.847">Your</span> <span begin="57.847" end="58.705">heart&apos;s</span> <span begin="58.705" end="1:00.380">golden</span> <span begin="1:00.380" end="1:01.245">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:01.245" end="1:03.517">beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的赤子之心是最美的王冠</span></p><p begin="1:03.832" end="1:20.259" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:03.832" end="1:04.700">Your</span> <span begin="1:04.700" end="1:06.375">naked</span> <span begin="1:06.375" end="1:07.254">soul</span> <span begin="1:07.254" end="1:08.141">is</span> <span begin="1:08.141" end="1:10.123">beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的美丽出淤泥而不染</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:11.905" end="1:20.259"><span begin="1:11.905" end="1:13.577">(Whoa</span> <span begin="1:15.005" end="1:16.980">Beautiful</span> <span begin="1:18.515" end="1:20.259">Whoa)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如此动人</span></span></p><p begin="1:21.968" end="1:23.682" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.968" end="1:23.682">Beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">美得令人窒息</span></p><p begin="1:49.292" end="2:01.523" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.292" end="1:51.120">Beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你本来就很美</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:52.768" end="2:01.523"><span begin="1:52.768" end="1:54